Reasoning: 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the use of reinforcement learning algorithms for optimizing traffic light control policy in intelligent transportation systems. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper specifically mentions the use of Deep Deterministic Policy Gradient (DDPG) algorithm. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with optimizing traffic flow in a transportation system. 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is relevant as the paper describes building a multi-agent system for traffic light control. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the effect of communication and coordination on the performance of the system.
